data.description: Beautiful home, featuring 3 Beds, 2 Baths, Liv/Fam Rm, Dining, Breakfast Bar, Screened Porch, 2 Car Garage, Big Back Yard with Shed, Open Patio with Pavers, Fruit Trees. This gorgeous home waits for you. It is Only 10-15 minutes from Downtown Ocala, CF College, Golf, shopping mall, Restaurants, the World Equestrian Center, about 5 minutes from the I-75 interstate, and all you can find in Ocala. Located In the very attractive community of The Fountains with very low HOA fees. Sale includes a one-year Home Warranty. Owner has a Florida Real Estate License.
